Like others have mentioned, this torrent is stuck at 99.9%. Only the AVI file is downloading.. the other text files are not (no loss there).  Don't let the 99.9% prevent you from downloading though... the avi file plays perfectly in media player and VLC Media player.  

There must be some glitch either with encoding, or in the torrent creation that is reporting false file size or preventing a complete download. But as I said, it is not affecting video quality... nor does there seem to be any missing chunks of video.  So, in my humble opinion, download with confidence, as per usual! :o)
